<Painkiller> is a drug:
    ingredients:
        Paracetamol 500.0 mg
    dosage safety:
        maximum single dose = 1000.0 mg
        minimum time between doses = 4 hours


<DrSmith> is an addressee:
    contact information:
        email is "drsmith@example.com"
    order of contacting:
        contact all addressees in parallel

<SymptomScore> is a number.

<AnalysisPlan> is a plan:
    during plan:
        context:
            timeframe: 2 years ago
            data: <SymptomScore>
        
        assess confidence of <SymptomScore>:
            > 90%:
                show message "High confidence in score".
            in all other cases:
                show message "Low confidence".

        assess count of <SymptomScore>:
            > 5:
                show message "Enough data points".
                ask "How do you feel?"
        
        show message to <DrSmith> "Analysis complete".
